{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/58/c6/5087_crt_sD1jd.jpg?r=1446190179","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/58/c6/5087_crt_sD1jd.jpg?r=1446190179","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/58/c6/5087_crt_sD1jd.jpg?r=1446190179","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/58/c6/5087_crt_sD1jd.jpg?r=1446190179"},"name":"ハウル","summary":"","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/2b/a1/4505_prsn_DzaWl.jpg?r=1746420589","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2b/a1/4505_prsn_DzaWl.jpg?r=1746420589","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/2b/a1/4505_prsn_DzaWl.jpg?r=1746420589","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/2b/a1/4505_prsn_DzaWl.jpg?r=1746420589"},"name":"木村拓哉","short_summary":"木村拓哉，1972年11月13日出生于日本东京都，日本男演员、歌手、声优。曾是日本男子组合SMAP的成员。隶属于STARTO ENTERTAINMENT事务所。昵称是“キムタク”。\r\n\r\n1987年11月，加入杰尼斯事务所，担任光GENJI的伴舞成员。1988年4月，与中居正广等5人组成SMAP组合。1991年9月，发行出道单曲《Can't Stop!! -LOVING-》，并于同年底随组合首次登上第42届NHK红白歌会的舞台。1992年，出演电视剧《是谁偷走我的心》，1993年，在电视剧《爱情白皮书》中自然的表演为他赢得了观众的口碑。1994年，凭借首部电影《足球风云》获得第7届日刊体育电影大奖的石原裕次郎新人奖。1996年，主演的电视剧《悠长假期》的最高瞬间收视率为43.8%而创下纪录。2000年，主演的电视剧《美丽人生》的最高单集收视率为41.3%而创下纪录；同年12月，与歌手工藤静香结婚。2001年，主演的电视剧《律政英雄》成为民放日剧史上唯一一部每集收视率均超过30%的电视剧；2006年，其主演的电影《武士的一分》获得第30届日本电影学院奖的13个奖项。截止2008年，木村拓哉连续15年获得《anan》杂志评选的“日本最受欢迎男性”排行榜的冠军。\r\n\r\n2016年12月31日，其所在组合SMAP正式解散，木村成为单飞艺人。2019年9月，宣布将作为歌手展开活动。2020年1月，发行个人首张专辑《Go with the Flow》。2024年1月，主演电影《传奇与蝴蝶》。\r\n\r\n截止2017年，木村拓哉是主演富士电视台黄金档月九剧次数最多的演员，共11次。","career":["artist","seiyu","actor"],"id":4505,"type":1,"locked":false},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/e0/d3/7296_prsn_1Lg6P.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e0/d3/7296_prsn_1Lg6P.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/e0/d3/7296_prsn_1Lg6P.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/e0/d3/7296_prsn_1Lg6P.jpg"},"name":"王凯","short_summary":"王凯，配音演员。1980年出生，毕业于北京电影学院02级高职配音班。","career":["seiyu"],"id":7296,"type":1,"locked":false},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/51/0f/33363_prsn_v6Yef.jpg?r=1692347824","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/51/0f/33363_prsn_v6Yef.jpg?r=1692347824","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/51/0f/33363_prsn_v6Yef.jpg?r=1692347824","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/51/0f/33363_prsn_v6Yef.jpg?r=1692347824"},"name":"Christian Bale","short_summary":"Christian Charles Philip Bale is a Welsh-American actor. Born in Haverfordwest, Wales, to English parents, he first caught the public eye at the age of 13, when he was cast in the starring role of Steven Spielberg's Empire of the Sun (1987). After a string of semi-successful feature films, he portrayed Wall Street banker and serial killer Patrick Bateman in American Psycho (2000) to widespread critical acclaim. His reputation for going great lengths to portray characters in films was first noted in the psychological thriller The Machinist (2004), where he lost 63 pounds (28.5 kg) to play the main lead role. Within six months he gained 100 lb (45 kg) to star as Batman in Christopher Nolan's Batman Begins (2005), The Dark Knight (2008) and The Dark Knight Rises (2012); the three films, The Dark Knight Trilogy, grossed over two billion dollars, making it the 8th highest-grossing film series. He is known for his intense method acting style, often transforming his body drastically to suit his chosen roles.","career":["seiyu","actor"],"id":33363,"type":1,"locked":false},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/dd/eb/78964_prsn_VmVvv.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/dd/eb/78964_prsn_VmVvv.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/dd/eb/78964_prsn_VmVvv.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/dd/eb/78964_prsn_VmVvv.jpg"},"name":"李勇","short_summary":"台湾男性配音员、广播节目主持人。","career":["seiyu"],"id":78964,"type":1,"locked":false},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/03/d7/82896_prsn_yKGiq.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/03/d7/82896_prsn_yKGiq.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/